Density, distribution, quantile and random generation function for the logitnormal distribution. Estimation of the mode and the first two moments. Estimation of distribution parameters.

name: r-logitnorm
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = '0.8.38' %}
{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}
{% set native = 'm2w64-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-logitnorm
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/logitnorm_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/logitnorm/logitnorm_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 38f55427955625d17ea5e92267d2549f3f2a21f3c3ee228d81c181dc80d05b07

build:
  merge_build_host: True  # [win]
  number: 1
  noarch: generic
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ posix }}zip               # [win]
    - cross-r-base {{ r_base }}    # [build_platform != target_platform]
  host:
    - r-base
  run:
    - r-base

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('logitnorm')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('logitnorm')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: https://CRAN.R-project.org/package=logitnorm
  license: GPL-2.0-only
  summary: Density, distribution, quantile and random generation function for the logitnormal
    distribution. Estimation of the mode and the first two moments. Estimation of distribution
    parameters.
  license_family: GPL2
  license_file:
    - '{{ environ["PREFIX"] }}/lib/R/share/licenses/GPL-2'

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r
